{"tid":2048011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN: 侵侵 全世界都笑緊我哋","createTime":"2020-06-02T13:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T13:31:42.000Z","uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d5f7d080ecf6ff8b8ceab6345d06db162daa8e","tid":2048011,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3er8nULW1t0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3er8nULW1t0&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=a5b26d3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3er8nULW1t0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）公佈一段特朗普在周一上午和美國各州州長的一次電話會議錄音，會議上特朗普對州長進行了猛烈抨擊，表示州長門最初不願意召集國民警衛隊，並 稱美國&ldquo;成了全世界的笑柄&rdquo;、&ldquo;整個世界都在嘲笑我們&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n 特朗普說道：&ldquo;你必須使用國民警衛隊來搞定一些人，但他們一開始並沒有這麼做，他們之後這麼做了...我就住在曼哈頓，我不知道曼哈頓發生了什麼，但是情況 是可怕的，必須要完全把控局勢，你們必須控制住。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"50c7226247fbc1bcfd9fd826afdb742d9f1e2f81","tid":2048011,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"又係既<br />\n鬼叫你次次出事地區都係民主黨州咩"},{"pid":"8217dc96574fc712868d0005e22d3ca19a8a5e21","tid":2048011,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"Trump 講嗰句有啲似往死裡打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}